{"tid":912201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鼻孔灌60公斤水黃牛流淚跪地 屠宰場老闆被捕","createTime":"2018-11-22T13:05:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T16:33:18.000Z","uid":29238,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"35db80a6f84069de277e087f6c1042c1bea29873","tid":912201,"uid":29238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T13:05:37.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】殘忍！近日，安徽滁州全椒、來安兩地有注水牛屠宰場被查獲，黃牛12小時被注水120斤，牛隻痛倒流淚下跪。附近村民稱，每天都有牛的慘叫聲。目前相關屠宰場已被取締，負責人也已被警方帶走。<br />\n<br />\n據報，位於安徽省全椒縣和來安縣的屠宰場，這些業者為了讓牛隻大量增重，將塑膠水管塞入牛鼻直達牛胃，並且在12小時內注水120斤（約60公斤），之後再將牠們宰殺販售，以製作「注水肉」，藉此在市場謀取暴利。黃牛因為經不起疼痛而無法站直，直接跪倒在地，明顯殘暴虐待動物。<br />\n<br />\n面對內地記者鏡頭，屠宰場老闆許先生竟然說，「反正進到屠宰場的牛都是要宰殺的，不管有沒有注水，最後牠們的結果都一樣，而且注水後的重量也沒增加多少，我們也不砸牠或打牠，所以牛不會痛。」<br />\n<br />\n事件曝光後，全縣市場監管、農委等多個部門單位組成聯合執法隊伍，對全縣農貿市場進行盤查，發現問題肉主要流向南京，監管局相關負責人目前已經到屠宰場取締，負責人也都被警方帶走。執法人員在屠宰場發現，注過水的活牛高達13頭，已屠宰的注水牛則有6頭，並且查獲銷售注水肉的6處攤位，逮捕29位嫌犯。<br />\n<br />\n事件曝光，引發網民怒斥：「建議給這個屠宰場老闆的胃裡注點水，再問他痛不痛」、「無良商家，為了一時利益，如此殘害動物，難道動物就沒有該有的權利嗎？」、「真有良知就不要吃牛肉」、「豬也是有被注水的，只是還沒發現而已」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正仆街"},{"pid":"91435b6b1a93f28b955adf69768a11fe40449180","tid":912201,"uid":29238,"like":1,"dislike":19,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T13:06:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gerqQ5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgerqQ5b.jpg&h=f811a509&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c24e68731f07c33f18107ef02787bdb8581843e","tid":912201,"uid":156363,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T13:07:12.000Z","msg":"慘過死"},{"pid":"8e80d3cad72f491873ae15eef46b05803d50542e","tid":912201,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T13:08:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b50cf224cbab95fd0d8b2a500f1db6bace3e419c","tid":912201,"uid":106810,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T13:10:33.000Z","msg":"你屌佢佢屌你食鵝肝"},{"pid":"e46fa52744bb9e48e06769ed06505a261ead0d24","tid":912201,"uid":66436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T13:16:51.000Z","msg":"為左令啲肉重d?"},{"pid":"12f1a56283444a83138203ea1995779baa32a422","tid":912201,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T13:17:51.000Z","msg":"but why"},{"pid":"308fb54015daa88825f847172728c274c7d9ab2d","tid":912201,"uid":183758,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T13:18:17.000Z","msg":"支那賤蓄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3540d1aab83fe2981bc566bd04b88469d6383ed","tid":912201,"uid":58387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T13:18:40.000Z","msg":"陰公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2660ba730548cf84ee2a9abf1723f8